    Combined with 4D Flow, it is now possible to noninvasively obtain accurate flow values and 3D
    anatomical data. Applications lie in the assessment of aneurysms, arteriovenous malformations
    (AVMs) and development of ischemic conditions in the head and neck.
  </p>
